snippet.title: Turbo Chicken Simulator - Announcement trailer
snippet.description:
Turbo Chicken Simulator is an immersive, open-world action RPG. It is the latest and greatest in high-tech Chicken Simulation technology. It is an upcoming game developed by Balkanware gamde development studio.

Add Turbo Chicken Simulator to your wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2569610/Turbo_Chicken_Simulator/

Check out the official website:
https://balkanware.org/turbo-chicken-simulator/
